A '''binary liquid''' was one of many materials used in the construction of [[Mandalorian armor/Legends|Mandalorian armor]]. It had to be combined with other liquids in order to construct the armor, a combination that led to a necessary chemical reaction. This made it beneficial in manufacturing.<ref name="Galaxies">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

